---
/*
  Pricing block: three cards with a featured center card.
  Uses Tailwind utilities to match spacing/typography of the demo.
*/
---
<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-12">
    <h2 id="pricing" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Pricing & Services</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Help Your Business Grow While Saving Money.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 (starter) -->
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white border-brand transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 
         hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.6)] hover:border-purple-700">
        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Maintenance and Operations</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold">$120 <span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500">/ instance</span></div>
        <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Aggregate Data Sources & 3rd Party Access</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Complete Data Privacy & Freedom</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Export Cloud Backed Data with Analysis</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Custom Url Prefix with OAuth Login</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Asynchronous Reporting with 24/7 access</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200" href="#signup">Register now</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured Card -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white pricing-featured border-2 border-brand transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 
         hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(168,85,247,0.6)] hover:border-purple-500">
        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Packaged Services Per Month</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">$1075 <span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500">/ month</span></div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Best Value</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Monthly Allotments of Cleaning, ETL, & Visualization</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Managed Dashboard with Data Exports</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> LLM Powered Insights for Data-Driven Decisions</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Automated Workflows & Process Improvement</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Improve & Expand Your Business</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-md bg-brand hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold" href="#signup">Register now</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 (enterprise) -->
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white border-brand transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 
         hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.6)] hover:border-purple-700">
        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Automation and Visualization Excess</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold">$350 <span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500">/ day</span></div>
        <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Prettify and Automate Data Collection & Analysis</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Custom Data Warehousing and Architecture</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Stunning and Interactive Visualizations</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Rigorous Mathematical & Statistical Basis</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> AI/ML Models and Insights on Your Business</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200" href="#signup">Register now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
